CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 23, 1939, pg. 10, reads: "Wynona Graves Fetes LaSalle Students and Friends at Dinner in Loendi - Colorful among the pre-Christmas festive events was the annual dinner given by Wynona Graves to her LaSalle students and friends in Loendi's beautiful dining room Saturday evening. The guests included many out-of-towners.  Top, left to right: Florine Robinson, Marian Stanton, Billy Jackson,....Out-of-towners, Sallie Young, Welch, W.Va.; Rosa Moore, New Jersey; Sarah Moss, New York; Velma Knappes, Canonsburg; Miss Jibbes. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Florine Robinson, Marian Stanton, and Billy Jackson, seated at table in Loendi Club for annual dinner given by Wynona Graves for LaSalle students and friends
